reviewText: Very well presented introduction to Neopolitan Mastiffs.  Very basic, would have liked more pictures or videos of Neos in action, how different they look as they grow, different cord etc.  overall well done basic information.

I cute Neopolitan Mastiff puppy is filmed, and the owner is talking about the Neopolitan Mastiff's characteristics, temperament, health problems in general. The information is brief and important, however there was not much new information. I also would have liked to see grown up Neopolitan Mastiffs.
